This paper is about distributed training for deep learning, which is a subfield of machine learning. The paper specifically focuses on improving the Stale Synchronous Parallel (SSP) paradigm by dynamically determining the staleness threshold at runtime. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing), cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms), cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing), and cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition).
